### ================
### Catalog service
### ================

### Browser all events with the venue and sessions data
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Events?$expand=venue,sessions

### Try to create an event (should fail - 405 Method Not Allowed)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Events
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "This should fail"
}

### ================
### Admin service
### ================

### Browse all events with everthing expanded
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events?$expand=sessions,registrations,venue

### Create new event
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "BTP Developer Day 2026",
    "description": "A one-day hand-on workshop for BTP developers",
    "startDate": "2026-10-15T09:00:00Z",
    "endDate": "2026-10-15T17:00:00Z",
    "maxCapacity": 100
}

### Try to create an event with invalid dates
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "BTP Developer Day 2026",
    "description": "A one-day hand-on workshop for BTP developers",
    "startDate": "2026-10-15T09:00:00Z",
    "endDate": "2026-10-12T17:00:00Z",
    "maxCapacity": 100
}

### Check events in admin service (should show attendeeCount and seatsRemaining)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events?$select=title,maxCapacity,attendeeCount,seatsRemaining

### ================
### Registration service
### ================

### Browse events (limited fields)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Events

### Create a registration
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Alice",
    "lastName": "Johnson",
    "email": "alice@example.com",
    "event_ID": "6ec0bd7f-11c0-43da-975e-2a8ad9ebae0b"
}

### Register with missing fields (should return multiple errors)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "event_ID": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6"
}

### Register for a draft event (should fail - not published)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Alice",
    "lastName": "Johnson",
    "email": "alice@example.com",
    "event_ID": "a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11"
}

### Register successfullyfor TechEd (published, has capacity)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Alice",
    "lastName": "Johnson",
    "email": "alice@example.com",
    "event_ID": "6ec0bd7f-11c0-43da-975e-2a8ad9ebae0b"
}
